title: LOVELY TENNESSEE HEIGHTS 2BR/1BA, ALL UTIL/WIFI INCL. Shorter term, OK
posting_body: ['Lovely Spacious Tennessee Heights NW 2BR/1BA.', 'Water, sewer, gas, electric, trash, wireless internet and cable included (a $300 value).', '4- OR 9-month lease, through December or May, OR 1 year.', 'Exposed brick, recessed lights, washer/dryer, dishwasher, Central AC, eat-in kitchen, gas stove, and backyard.', 'Furnished with 2 beds (queen and full), couch, television, microwave, kitchen table, etc. Includes bedding and dishes.', 'Wash and dry your clothes in your unit for free.', 'In addition to a shower, bathroom has a tub.', 'Near everything!', 'Bike lane on the street in front of the house and 3 to 5 blocks to subways.', 'Walking distance to social gathering spots, grocery stores, coffee shops, a green dry cleaner, vegan eateries and international restaurants, 2 blocks to a gym, tennis courts, soccer fields, a trendy café open until midnight and 2.5 blocks to bicycle rentals!', 'TRULY in the heart of the city.', 'No pets.', 'No smoking.', 'No amenity fee.', 'Through December 2022, $2,500 per month.', 'Through May 2023, $2,400.', '1-year lease, $2,350.', 'Off street parking additional.', '3600 block 11th Street NW.', 'CONTACT BY PHONE anytime, not email,', 'show contact info', '.']
